ed or stuck outside the state are given assistance through DBT mode. Accordingly, the state govt. will start distribution of milk powder soon along with the Jharkhand Mukhyamantri Ration Yojana.For milk distribution, district administration has given cheque of Rs. 10 lakh to CM Relief Fund. Parle-G biscuit company has also provided 2 lakh biscuit packets and Lifebuoy company has provided 10,000 soaps. All the persons, societies, companies and other sections must fight in collaboration to defeat Coronavirus pandemic.What is Containment Area Containment Area is that particular place where Coronavirus (COVID-19) patients are present. The state govt. then seal an area of 1 to 3 kilometers nearby that particular area of a district.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}